users
Your app’s internal user record linked to Clerk.

id: UUID (your DB ID)
clerkId: Clerk user ID (string like user_xxx)
email, name, imageUrl, timezone(in future we change it)
billing fields:
plan: "free" or "pro"
stripeCustomerId: cus_... (optional)
stripeSubscriptionId: sub_... (optional)
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
habits
A habit definition (not the daily completion).

belongs to: one user (userId)
fields: name, category, frequency, targetFrequency, color, icon, isActive(use in delete)
streak cache: currentStreak, longestStreak
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
habit_logs
One habit’s activity for one day.
belongs to: one habit (habitId)
unique: (habitId, date) so you can’t create duplicates
fields: date (YYYY-MM-DD), completed, completedCount, note